milestones.description: Kevin Hurdle and Leverock's 25-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Kwame Tucker and O'Brien
This is the lowest match aggregate (270) involving teams Bermuda & Kenya in ODIs
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for BMUDA, going past Romaine

stories.title: Logie: 'It's difficult to know where we go from here'
stories.subTitle: Bermuda crash in opening match
stories.summary: Gus Logie, Bermuda's coach, cast a deflated figure after watching his side crash to a ten-wicket defeat by Kenya in the opening match of the World Cricket League

stories.title: Rampant Kenyans rout dismal Bermuda
stories.subTitle: Bermuda v Kenya, WCL, Nairobi
stories.summary: Hosts Kenya made a rousing start to the World Cricket League at Nairobi's Jaffreys Sports Club, destroying a dismal Bermuda by ten wickets in as one-sided a contest as the tournament is likely to produce
